---
title: Mexican Pork Steak & Smokey Aioli with Charred Lemon & Cucumber Salad
description: Tonight, let the flavours of Mexico take over your BBQ. Grilled to juicy perfection, the pork is seasoned with Mexican spices and paired with a charred lemon for a burst of citrus. A fresh cucumber salad adds crispness, while a drizzle of smoky aioli lends it a creamy finish. It’s a fiesta of flavours, right off the grill!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
